<h1>Laws & Policies</h1>
<dl>

<dt>
NOLO: Law for All
</dt>
<dd>
Provides legal information explained so you can understand it, even if you didn't go to law school.
</dd>
<dd>
&lt;<a href="http://www.nolo.com/" target="_blank">http://www.nolo.com/</a>&gt;
</dd>

<dt>
Bitlaw: A Resource on Technology Law
</dt>
<dd>
Internet resource that focuses on copyright, patent, trademark and Internet law.
</dd>
<dd>
&lt;<a href="http://www.bitlaw.com" target="_blank">http://www.bitlaw.com/</a>&gt;
</dd>

<dt>
UCLA Library Copyright Policy
</dt>
