<h1>Overviews & Other Stuff</h1>
<dl>

<dt>
Copyright Website
</dt>
<dd>Informative and fun&mdash;really. You can listen to George Harrison's "My Sweet Lord" alongside of the Chiffons "He's So Fine" and see if you agree with the court's decision. There are a lot of other songs to compare, as well as video clips, and information about famous cases that focused on digital media. Covers a variety of copyright issues.</dd>
<dd>
&lt;<a href="http://www.benedict.com/" target="_blank">http://www.benedict.com/</a>&gt;</dd>

<dt>
Patent Caf&eacute;
</dt>
